tags: clap, hand, room, sm57, tiled
description:
Hand clapped several times in succession then edited into individual hits for programming. The same pair of hands, same place same time. recorded with Sure SM57 microphone placed over conga drum. Ringing can be heard of drum and room. natural sound.

Suggested uses, rotate claps in succession for a feely rhythm or perhaps play two at once or more for effect, de-tune some etc.
